---
layout: base.njk
title: "The Right Words for Life's Biggest Moments"
description: "The Quiet Pen helps you write wedding vows, speeches, and letters that sound like you — through guided workbooks and thoughtful, human editing. Your voice, quietly supported."
---
{% from "icons.njk" import check, arrowRight, featherIllustration, quoteMark, plus %}

<section class="hero" data-hero>
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">A Writing Studio for Meaningful Moments</span>
      <h1>The right words for life's biggest moments.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Whether you're promising forever, raising a glass, honoring a career, celebrating someone
        you love, or saying goodbye, The Quiet Pen helps you express what matters most — in your
        own voice.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/workbook/">Browse Wedding Workbook</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/services/">Explore Writing Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-art reveal reveal-delay-2" aria-hidden="true">
      {{ featherIllustration() }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="stat-number" data-count-to="500" data-suffix="+">0</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Vows &amp; speeches written</span>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="stat-number" data-count-to="4.9" data-suffix="/5">0</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Average client rating</span>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="stat-number" data-count-to="3" data-suffix="+">0</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Revision rounds included</span>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <span class="stat-number" data-count-to="100" data-suffix="%">0</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Written in your own voice</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt" id="workbook-spotlight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Flagship Guide</span>
        <h2>Write Wedding Vows You'll Actually Want to Say</h2>
        <p class="lede">
          This isn't a collection of vows to copy. It's a guided writing experience —
          worksheets, prompts, and gentle structure that help you discover the vows only you
          could have written, then say them with confidence.
        </p>
        <ul class="stack" style="gap: 0.6rem; margin: var(--space-md) 0;">
          <li class="cluster">{{ check("icon-check") }} <span>Brainstorming prompts that surface real memories</span></li>
          <li class="cluster">{{ check("icon-check") }} <span>A tone-and-voice guide, so it sounds like you</span></li>
          <li class="cluster">{{ check("icon-check") }} <span>Printable worksheets and a step-by-step editing checklist</span></li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/workbook/">See Inside the Workbook {{ arrowRight("icon-arrow") }}</a>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="preview-gallery">
          <div class="preview-page">
            <span class="badge">01 &middot; Finding Your Story</span>
            <div class="preview-line" style="margin-top:1rem;"></div>
            <div class="preview-line short"></div>
            <div class="preview-line tall"></div>
            <span class="preview-page-label">Prompt: What moment made you certain?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="preview-page">
            <span class="badge">06 &middot; Finding Your Voice</span>
            <div class="preview-line" style="margin-top:1rem;"></div>
            <div class="preview-line short"></div>
            <div class="preview-line tall"></div>
            <span class="preview-page-label">Worksheet: Say it out loud, then write it down</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="future-workbooks">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">Life's Biggest Moments</span>
      <h2>One studio, for every moment worth writing about.</h2>
      <p class="lede" style="margin-inline:auto;">
        Weddings are where we started. These guided workbooks are on their way next — each one
        built with the same care.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-4">
      {% for book in workbooks %}
      <div class="book-card reveal reveal-delay-{{ loop.index0 % 4 + 1 }}">
        {% if book.status == "available" %}
          <a href="{{ book.href }}" aria-label="{{ book.title }}">
            <div class="book-cover is-flagship">
              <div class="book-cover-inner">
                <svg class="book-cover-mark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><path d="M8 24 L22 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                <div class="book-cover-title">{{ book.title }}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        {% else %}
          <div class="book-cover">
            <div class="book-cover-inner">
              <svg class="book-cover-mark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><path d="M8 24 L22 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
              <div class="book-cover-title">{{ book.title }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="book-meta">
          {% if book.status == "available" %}
            <span class="badge badge-accent">Available Now</span>
          {% else %}
            <span class="badge">Coming Soon</span>
          {% endif %}
          <h3>{{ book.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ book.description }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt" id="services-teaser">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">Writing Services</span>
      <h2>Sometimes you want a guide. Sometimes you want a hand.</h2>
      <p class="lede" style="margin-inline:auto;">
        For moments that call for more than a workbook, our writers work directly with you —
        listening carefully, then helping you shape what you already know you want to say.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-3">
      <div class="card reveal">
        <h3>Review &amp; Refine</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">You've written a draft. We help with grammar, flow, clarity, and
          emotional impact — without losing your voice.</p>
        <a href="/services/#review-refine">Learn more {{ arrowRight("icon-arrow") }}</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h3>Custom Writing</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">A guided questionnaire, one writer, and a piece crafted from
          scratch in your voice — with a full revision included.</p>
        <a href="/services/#custom-writing">Learn more {{ arrowRight("icon-arrow") }}</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h3>Signature Experience</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">Our most thorough offering: a consultation, multiple revisions,
          priority turnaround, and a keepsake printable.</p>
        <a href="/services/#signature-experience">Learn more {{ arrowRight("icon-arrow") }}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/services/">Compare All Services</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="process">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">Our Process</span>
      <h2>Quiet, careful, and entirely yours.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-step reveal">
        <h4>Share your story</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">A short questionnaire or a conversation — however you'd rather tell it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h4>We listen carefully</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">We read between the lines for the details that actually matter to you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h4>We thoughtfully write</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">A first draft, written to sound like you on your most articulate day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal">
        <h4>You review</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">Read it aloud. Sit with it. Tell us what feels off, if anything does.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h4>Together we refine</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">We adjust tone, trim length, and sharpen the moments that matter most.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h4>You confidently speak</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">The words are ready. So are you. The moment is entirely yours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-dark" id="philosophy">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Philosophy</span>
        <h2>Words often outlive the moment.</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">
          A wedding video gets watched a few times. A retirement toast gets mentioned at family
          dinners for years. A letter gets kept in a drawer and re-read on hard days. The moments
          themselves pass quickly — the words spoken during them tend to stay.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted">
          That's why we treat this work carefully. Not because the writing should sound
          impressive, but because it should sound like <em>you</em>, on a day when it counted.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <p class="guiding-principle">
          "{{ site.guidingPrinciple }}"
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
          You already have the feelings. We simply help you express them. Our goal isn't to
          replace your voice — it's to help you discover it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">In Their Words</span>
      <h2>The best compliment we receive: "That sounded exactly like me."</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-3">
      {% for t in testimonials %}
      {% if loop.index <= 3 %}
      <div class="testimonial-card reveal reveal-delay-{{ loop.index }}">
        <div class="testimonial-stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-quote">{{ quoteMark("icon-quote") }}{{ t.quote }}</p>
        <div class="testimonial-person">
          <div class="avatar-placeholder" style="background: var(--{{ t.color }});">{{ t.initials }}</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-name">{{ t.name }}</div>
            <div class="testimonial-detail">{{ t.detail }}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt" id="sample-advice">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">From the Journal</span>
      <h2>Thoughtful answers, not finished speeches.</h2>
      <p class="lede" style="margin-inline:auto;">
        We'd rather teach you something useful than hand you a script. A few places to start:
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-3">
      <div class="card reveal">
        <h3><a href="/blog/how-long-should-wedding-vows-be/">How Long Should Wedding Vows Be?</a></h3>
        <p class="text-muted">The honest answer, plus how to tell if yours are running long.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h3><a href="/blog/how-to-write-a-speech-that-sounds-like-you/">Writing a Speech That Sounds Like You</a></h3>
        <p class="text-muted">A practical approach to finding your own voice on paper.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h3><a href="/blog/biggest-mistakes-wedding-speakers-make/">The Biggest Mistakes Wedding Speakers Make</a></h3>
        <p class="text-muted">And the simple fixes for each one.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/blog/">Visit the Journal</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="faq-preview">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="section-header center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">Common Questions</span>
      <h2>Good to know before you start.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <details class="accordion-item" name="faq-preview">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger">
          <span>Will my vows actually sound like me?</span>
          {{ plus() }}
        </summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">
          That's the entire point. The workbook is built around your memories, your words, and
          your way of speaking — we never hand you generic lines to copy. If you work with a
          writer directly, every draft is built from your own answers and revised until it
          sounds unmistakably like you.
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="accordion-item" name="faq-preview">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger">
          <span>I'm not a good writer. Will that be a problem?</span>
          {{ plus() }}
        </summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">
          Not at all — that's exactly who we built this for. Most people who come to us
          already know what they want to say; they just haven't found a way to put it into
          words yet. That's the part we help with.
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="accordion-item" name="faq-preview">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger">
          <span>Is this only for weddings?</span>
          {{ plus() }}
        </summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">
          Weddings are where we started, and where our workbook library lives today. Our
          writing services already support speeches, toasts, and letters for other
          milestones, with more guided workbooks on the way.
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="accordion-item" name="faq-preview">
        <summary class="accordion-trigger">
          <span>How private is this process?</span>
          {{ plus() }}
        </summary>
        <div class="accordion-panel-content">
          Completely. Everything you share is confidential, used only to write your piece,
          and never shared, published, or reused without your permission.
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/faq/">Read All FAQs</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="newsletter reveal" data-newsletter-form-wrapper>
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--eucalyptus);">Stay in Touch</span>
        <h2>Thoughtful writing advice, sent occasionally.</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">
          No noise, no daily emails — just useful guidance on writing for the moments that matter,
          plus a first look when new workbooks launch.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <form class="newsletter-form" data-newsletter-form>
          <label class="sr-only" for="newsletter-email">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" id="newsletter-email" name="email" placeholder="you@email.com" required />
          <button class="btn btn-accent" type="submit">Subscribe</button>
        </form>
        <p class="newsletter-note">We respect your inbox. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
        <p class="form-success" role="status">{{ check() }} You're on the list — welcome.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
